<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Reschedule Request Submitted</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3a8a 0%, #3b82f6 100%);
            padding: 30px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .logo {
            max-width: 150px;
            height: auto;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .header h1 {
            color: #ffffff;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 0;
        }
        
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        
        .status-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #f59e0b;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }
        
        .greeting {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #1f2937;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        
        .message {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #4b5563;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }
        
        .doctor-info {
            background-color: #f0f9ff;
            border: 1px solid #bae6fd;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        
        .doctor-info h3 {
            color: #1e3a8a;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 16px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        
        .doctor-info h3::before {
            content: "üë®‚Äç‚öïÔ∏è";
            margin-right: 10px;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        
        .doctor-name {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1e3a8a;
        }
        
        .schedule-comparison {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        
        .schedule-box {
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        
        .schedule-box.original {
            border-left: 4px solid #dc2626;
        }
        
        .schedule-box.requested {
            border-left: 4px solid #059669;
        }
        
        .schedule-title {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        
        .schedule-title.original::before {
            content: "üìÖ";
            margin-right: 8px;
        }
        
        .schedule-title.requested::before {
            content: "üîÑ";
            margin-right: 8px;
        }
        
        .schedule-title.original {
            color: #dc2626;
        }
        
        .schedule-title.requested {
            color: #059669;
        }
        
        .schedule-detail {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 8px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }
        
        .schedule-detail:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        
        .schedule-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #374151;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        .schedule-value {
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        .status-info {
            background-color: #eff6ff;
            border: 1px solid #bfdbfe;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        
        .status-info h3 {
            color: #1e3a8a;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 16px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        
        .status-info h3::before {
            content: "‚è≥";
            margin-right: 10px;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        
        .status-info ul {
            margin-left: 20px;
            color: #374151;
        }
        
        .status-info li {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        
        .appointment-id {
            background-color: #f1f5f9;
            border: 1px solid #cbd5e1;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 12px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .appointment-id strong {
            color: #1e3a8a;
        }
        
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3a8a 0%, #3b82f6 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 14px 28px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .cta-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(30, 58, 138, 0.3);
        }
        
        .footer {
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            padding: 25px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }
        
        .footer p {
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .contact-info {
            color: #1e3a8a;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .content {
                padding: 25px 20px;
            }
            
            .header {
                padding: 20px 15px;
            }
            
            .schedule-comparison {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 15px;
            }
            
            .schedule-detail {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: flex-start;
                text-align: left;
            }
            
            .schedule-value {
                margin-top: 5px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <img src="https://sidclinic.com/logo.jpeg" alt="SID Clinic Logo" class="logo">
            <h1>Reschedule Request Submitted</h1>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <div class="status-badge">‚è∞ Request Submitted</div>
            
            <div class="greeting">Dear {{patientName}},</div>
            
            <div class="message">
                Your reschedule request has been submitted successfully. We've sent the request to 
                your doctor for review and approval. You'll receive a notification once they respond.
            </div>
            
            <div class="doctor-info">
                <h3>Doctor Information</h3>
                <div class="doctor-name">Dr. {{doctorName}}</div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="schedule-comparison">
                <div class="schedule-box original">
                    <div class="schedule-title original">Original Schedule</div>
                    
                    <div class="schedule-detail">
                        <span class="schedule-label">Date:</span>
                        <span class="schedule-value">{{originalDate}}</span>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="schedule-detail">
                        <span class="schedule-label">Time:</span>
                        <span class="schedule-value">{{originalTime}}</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="schedule-box requested">
                    <div class="schedule-title requested">Requested New Schedule</div>
                    
                    <div class="schedule-detail">
                        <span class="schedule-label">Date:</span>
                        <span class="schedule-value">{{newDate}}</span>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="schedule-detail">
                        <span class="schedule-label">Time:</span>
                        <span class="schedule-value">{{newTime}}</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="status-info">
                <h3>What Happens Next?</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Your doctor will review the reschedule request</li>
                    <li>You'll receive an email notification of their decision</li>
                    <li>If approved, your appointment will be updated automatically</li>
                    <li>If rejected, your original appointment time will remain unchanged</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="appointment-id">
                <strong>Appointment ID:</strong> #{{appointmentId}}
            </div>
            
            <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" class="cta-button">View Appointment Details</a>
            
            <div class="message">
                Please note that your original appointment time is still confirmed until the doctor 
                responds to your reschedule request. We'll keep you updated on the status.
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Thank you for choosing SID Clinic for your healthcare needs.</p>
            <p class="contact-info">Need help? Contact us at support@sidclinic.com</p>
            <p>¬© 2024 SID Clinic. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>



